description:
Imagine being a Christian for years – faithfully attending church, hearing sermons every week, paying tithe – yet hearing Jesus say on the day of judgment, “I never knew you”? Unthinkable! Yet Jesus taught that’s what will happen for many, even those who’ve spent their lives thinking they’re doing Him service. Why?

Authentic Christianity is not just finding Jesus but knowing Jesus, living with Christ, and growing in a relationship with Him until you’re one with Him. So, how do you do it? What method does God use to make you like Him? What is your part in the process? Pastor Pavel Goia shares lessons from the Bible and real-life stories to illustrate how to know Jesus personally. Discover what knowing Jesus is all about!
